summary: LETTER FROM JERRY SHIPMAN (OK) REGARDING NHTSA'S EARLY WARNING REPORTING (EWR) REGULATIONS. MR SHIPMAN OPPOSED THE ISSUANCE OF QUARTERLY EARLY WARNING  REPORT REGULATIONS BECAUSE IT WOULD PUT MANUFACTURER'S OF SMALL-TO-MEDIUM TRAILERS OUT OF BUSINESS, S10-0303(BREBBER SSGN). *AK           *JB
